{"name":"Experienced Forager","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;You know where to find mother natures best kept sustenance. Each day during your daily preparations, you gain a number of batches of restorative food equal to your Survival Proficiency bonus. This food can be anything within the nearby area. For instance, if you are camping out in the wilderness, it could be from a local berry bush, or pieces of small game. Each batch acts as an item of negligible  bulk with the following ability: [A] Interact: You consume the food and heal for 2d6 Health Points.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis healing increases to 3d6 at Expert, 4d6 at Master, and 6d6 at Legendary Proficiency.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:33555329,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;28&quot;:1}\">You know where to find mother natures best kept sustenance. Each day during your daily preparations, you gain a number of batches of restorative food equal to your Survival Proficiency bonus. This food can be anything within the nearby area. For instance, if you are camping out in the wilderness, it could be from a local berry bush, or pieces of small game. Each batch acts as an item of negligible bulk with the following ability: [A] Interact: You consume the food and heal for 2d6 Health Points.<br /><br />This healing increases to 3d6 at Expert, 4d6 at Master, and 6d6 at Legendary Proficiency.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.713,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"bonus"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"defau