{"name":"Mostly Dead","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Trigger: You just used Not the Kidneys\\n\\nAfter activating Not the Kidneys, you act in such a way as to appear dead to any foes. Make a Deception check against any visible hostile creatures Perception DC. Any creatures that did not see you activate Not the Kidneys automatically believe you to be dead until you take an action they can perceive.\\n\\nSuccess: The creature believes you to be dead\\nFailure: The creature does not fall for your trickery&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:33555329,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;28&quot;:1}\">Trigger: You just used Not the Kidneys<br /><br />After activating Not the Kidneys, you act in such a way as to appear dead to any foes. Make a Deception check against any visible hostile creatures Perception DC. Any creatures that did not see you activate Not the Kidneys automatically believe you to be dead until you take an action they can perceive.<br /><br />Success: The creature believes you to be dead</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Trigger: You just used Not the Kidneys\\n\\nAfter activating Not the Kidneys, you act in such a way as to appear dead to any foes. Make a Deception check against any visible hostile creatures Perception DC. Any creatures that did not see you activate Not the Kidneys automatically believe you to be dead until you take an action they can perceive.\\n\\nSuccess: The creature believes you to be dead\\nFailure: The creature does not fall for your trickery&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:33555329,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;28&quot;:1}\"><