{"name":"Unfathomable Conviction","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Trigger: An effect causes you to roll a Will save, or an effect with the mental trait targets you\\n\\nYour mind is an impenetrable fortress of strange and foreign ideas. The triggering creature makes a will save against your occultism DC.\\n\\nFailure: The creature sees an inner fear held by it inside your mind. It is frightened 1 until the start of it's next turn.\\nCritical Failure: The creature is unable to comprehend the imagery it sees inside your mind, and is filled with a primal fear. It is frightened 2 until the start of it's next turn.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:33555329,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;28&quot;:1}\">Trigger: An effect causes you to roll a Will save, or an effect with the mental trait targets you<br /><br />Your mind is an impenetrable fortress of strange and foreign ideas. The triggering creature makes a will save against your occultism DC.<br /><br />Failure: The creature sees an inner fear held by it inside your mind. It is frightened 1 until the start of it's next turn.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Trigger: An effect causes you to roll a Will save, or an effect with the mental trait targets you\\n\\nYour mind is an impenetrable fortress of strange and foreign ideas. The triggering creature makes a will save against your occultism DC.\\n\\nFailure: The creature sees an inner fear held by it inside your mind. It is frightened 1 until the start of it's next turn.\\nCritical Failure: The creature is unable to comprehend the imagery it sees inside your mind, and is filled with a primal fear. It is frightened 2 until the start of it's next turn.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:33555329,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;28&quot;:1}\"><br />Critical Failure: The creature is unable to comprehend the imagery it sees inside your mind, and is filled with a primal fear. It is frightened 2 until the start of it's next turn.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["general","incapacitation","mental","skill"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.713,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"skill"},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ajNtWZ644V4dHnNv":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.surles-feats.oWYgubbdkVl4crZv"}},"_id":"Rpd5IBJ36QqTVSps"}
